anhu daniY~N","text_ar":"كُلُّ دَنِىٍّ دُوَنهُ دَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is a relation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a friend, nearer than every"},{"kind":"text","text":"other"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relation,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"friend;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like another prov., namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna kul~i qurayobaY qurobaY","text_ar":"دُونَ كُلِّ قُرَيْبَى قُرْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", for the meaning and application of which see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrb","text_ar":"قرب"},{"kind":"text","text":": Freytag renders it, “ Quod attinet ad quemlibet propinquum (amicum), præter eum est propinquus:” (Arab. Prov. ii. 357:) and he adds, “ Proverbii sensus esse videtur: Quilibet propinquus seu amicus unicus non est; sed præter eum est alius ”]: (T, Meyd:) so says AZ. (Meyd.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adonaY","text_ar":"اَدْنَى"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  As an epithet applied to a man, signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Weak; contemptible;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see 1, near the end of the paragraph: [but J says that] as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwnN","text_ar":"دُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daniYo'N","text_ar":"دَنِىْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoniyaA='u","text_ar":"اَدْنِيَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, M.) [In the CK, by a mistranscription mentioned above (voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daniYa","text_ar":"دَنِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"danoYN","text_ar":"دَنْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is made to signify the same.]"}],"source_refs":["T","S","Meyd"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AF%D9%86%D9%89/","headword_ar":"دُنَى","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_48","lexicon_en":"Sultan Qaboos Encyclopedia of Arab Names (Sultan Qaboos University, 1985)","lexicon_ar":"موسوعة السلطان قابوس لأسماء العرب","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=112175#820405","body_html":"دُنَى<br>من (د ن و) جمع دُنْيا: العالم."}]}}